searchString = "Run State" if evt.summary.find(searchString) >= 0: value = evt.summary[evt.summary.find("current value ")+14:len(evt.summary)-1] status = "BLAH" val = int(float(value)) if val == -1: evt.severity = 2 status = "Unknown" if val == 0: evt.severity = 3 status = "Shutdown" if val == 1: evt.severity = 3 status = "Unavailable" if val == 2: evt.severity = 4 status = "Stopped" if val == 3: evt.severity = 0 status = "Online" if val == 4: evt.severity = 0 status = "Running" evt.summary = evt.component+" is "+status
